        "content": "Hey there — I’m here to help you build an AI content agent that really *gets* your voice and goals. Think of this like a deep, friendly chat to make sure we’re aligned before we launch.\n\nLet’s start with the big picture: What’s the *main goal* you want this agent to help you achieve? Is it to grow your audience, drive traffic to a site, build a personal brand, or something else? What would “success” look like for you in the first 30 days?",
